test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[5]]
  Right contains one more item: [5]
  Full diff:
  - [[5]]
  + []
test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[5], [5], [5...[5], [5], ...]
  Right contains 7 more items, first extra item: [5]
  Full diff:
  - [[5], [5], [5], [5], [5], [5], [5]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 1 == 5
 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
